==花絮==
该片曾在[[曼谷|曼谷]]、[[桂林市|桂林市]]、[[浙江省|浙江省]][[横店影视城|横店影视城]]、[[香港|香港]]等地取景，一共花费预算$21,000,000。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0398913/business | title=Business Data for DOA: Dead or Alive | publisher=Internet Movie Database | accessdate=2006-08-28 | archive-date=2017-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170410041103/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0398913/business | dead-url=no }}</ref><!-- "the first Western production shot largely in China's Hengdian World Studios" -->

该片上映之后，因性感火辣美女、动作招式华丽而吸引大批观众，票房大丰收，一共$7,516,532。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=doadeadoralive.htm |title=DOA: Dead or Alive (2007)<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-04-05 |archive-date=2018-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625144922/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=doadeadoralive.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/2007-08-29/02201693744.shtml |title=元奎带美女杀入暑期档 《生死格斗》票房不俗 |accessdate=2007 |publisher=新浪网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407085452/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/2007-08-29/02201693744.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://yule.sohu.com/20070606/n250418191.shtml |title=导演元奎拍《生死格斗》 华丽武打招式吸引观众 |accessdate=2007 |publisher=搜狐网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407100742/http://yule.sohu.com/20070606/n250418191.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://yule.sohu.com/20070817/n251645895.shtml |title=《生死格斗》将性感出击 最具魅惑电影风靡全球 |accessdate=2007 |publisher=搜狐网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304225912/http://yule.sohu.com/20070817/n251645895.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

邹兆龙精通[[跆拳道|跆拳道]]，同时是[[空手道|空手道]]黑带；2007年6月24日，该片在中国大陆上映。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2007-08-24/13151687858.shtml |title=元奎率高手“生死格斗” 游戏大片今日上映(图) |accessdate=2007 |publisher=新浪网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2016-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817071919/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2007-08-24/13151687858.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>该片是元奎进军国际影坛的第二部电影作品。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2007-08/25/content_147348.htm|title=元奎《生死格斗》首映|accessdate=2007|publisher=京华网|work=|language=zh-hans|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407080352/http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2007-08/25/content_147348.htm|archivedate=2014-04-07}}</ref>编剧曾执笔《[[风月俏佳人|风月俏佳人]]》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://yule.sohu.com/20070824/n251752369.shtml |title=元奎执导动作片《生死格斗》 8月24日全面公映 |accessdate=2007 |publisher=搜狐网 |work= |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304221937/http://yule.sohu.com/20070824/n251752369.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

